ing="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Live-Odyssey.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Live-Odyssey.-Credit-PRESS-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Live-Odyssey.-Credit-PRESS-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Live-Odyssey.-Credit-PRESS-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Live-Odyssey.-Credit-PRESS-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Live-Odyssey.-Credit-PRESS-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/David-Bowie">大卫·鲍伊（David Bowie）</a> ，<a href="/artists/Oasis">绿洲（Oasis）</a> ，<a href="/artists/Arctic-Monkeys">北极猴子（Arctic Monkeys）</a>等人将被包括在伦敦全新的“现场奥德赛”身临其境中。</p><p>将于2025年5月在卡姆登（Camden）开幕，“现场奥德赛”（Live Odyssey）先前被描述为“庆祝英国音乐丰富的挂毯，为各个年龄段的音乐爱好者提供独特的体验，以“对塑造英国的声音的开创性致敬”。</p><p>沉浸式和互动的体验将为塑造英国的声音的壮丽致敬。</p><p>该吸引力 - 将展览，展览博物馆和现场经验结合在一起 - 将通过一个两个半小时的冒险来吸引与会者在六十年的音乐中，捕捉英国音乐的演变，从60年代和70年代的早期，再到90年代的英国爆炸式爆炸，到了90年代的英国爆炸式。 </p><figure id="attachment_3833368" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3833368" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3833368" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/libertines_hologram_live_odyssey.jpg" alt="Libertines成为Camden的新现场奥德赛音乐体验的全息图。图片来源：新闻/现场奥德赛" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/libertines_hologram_live_odyssey.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/libertines_hologram_live_odyssey-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/libertines_hologram_live_odyssey-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/libertines_hologram_live_odyssey-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/libertines_hologram_live_odyssey-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/libertines_hologram_live_odyssey-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3833368" class="wp-caption-text"> Libertines成为Camden的新现场奥德赛音乐体验的全息图。图片来源：新闻/现场奥德赛</figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3843531" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3843531" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3843531" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Libertines-Live-Odyssey-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="自由主义者的“活漫游”。信用：出版" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Libertines-Live-Odyssey-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Libertines-Live-Odyssey-Credit-PRESS-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Libertines-Live-Odyssey-Credit-PRESS-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Libertines-Live-Odyssey-Credit-PRESS-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Libertines-Live-Odyssey-Credit-PRESS-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Libertines-Live-Odyssey-Credit-PRESS-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3843531" class="wp-caption-text">自由主义者的“活漫游”。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><p>粉丝将穿过六个不同的房间，每个房间都会在不同的音乐时代沉浸在客人中，并重新创建定义每个十年的景点，声音和文化时刻。现场房间和毗邻的酒吧之间都有运动的自由，因此人们可以一路聚会。</p><p> Included in the list of acts set to appear as holograms are the <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-libertines-become-holograms-for-new-live-odssey-experience-in-camden-3833287">previously revealed Libertines</a> , <a href="/artists/The-Beatles">The Beatles</a> , <a href="/artists/The-Rolling-Stones">The Rolling Stones</a> , <a href="/artists/The-Who">The Who</a> , <a href="/artists/Led-Zeppelin">Led Zeppelin</a> , <a href="/artists/Queen">Queen</a> , <a href="/artists/Sex-Pistols">Sex Pistols</a> , <a href="/artists/Kate-Bush">Kate Bush</a> , <a href="/artists/The-Smiths">The Smiths</a> , <a href="/artists/Duran-Duran">Duran Duran</a> , <a href="/artists/Eurythmics">Eurythmics</a> , <a href="/artists/Blur">Blur</a> , <a href="/artists/Radiohead">Radiohead</a> , <a href="/artists/Spice-Girls">Spice Girls</a> , <a href="/artists/Coldplay">Coldplay</a> , <a href="/artists/Amy-Winehouse">Amy Winehouse</a> , <a href="/artists/Adele">Adele</a> , <a href="/artists/Harry-Styles">Harry Styles</a> , <a href="/artists/Ed-Sheeran">Ed Sheeran</a> , <a href="/artists/Dua-Lipa">Dua Lipa</a> and <a href="/artists/Stormzy">Stormzy</a> .</p><p> “ Live Odyssey”还具有以前看不见的现场镜头和英国充满活力的音乐界的真实摄影作品。艺术家的传统物品也将不断变化，例如列侬的“ Imagine”唱片的鲍伊（Bowie）的麦克风与原始专辑Art一起，其中包括甲壳虫乐队的神奇神秘之旅，凯特·布什（Kate Bush）的“整个故事”和“整个故事”和“滚石乐队”“慢速滚动”。</p><p> “ Live Odyssey”的创意总监Gary Prosser谈到新闻稿时说：“ Live Odyssey不仅是对英国音乐丰富的挂毯的致敬；这是对社区，创造力和激情定义我们现场音乐界的庆祝活动。通过将创新技术与现场表演的精神融合在一起，我们正在创建一个空间，粉丝们可以与过去的传说联系在一起，同时激发明天的才华。 “现场奥德赛”不仅仅是一个场所。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DGTn8CsKlRS/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; mar